PrecisAmendment to the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS (Schedule No. 260) clarifying the condition which wheel nuts, wheel discs and hub caps installed on passenger cars and multipurpose passenger vehicles must comply with, to not incorporate winged projections that extend beyond the plane defined by the outer extremity of the wheel rim.
